wherein the Protector Unit determines that a particular IoT device is compromised or malfunctioning, based on Machine Learning (ML) analysis of both (i) control messages monitored by the UP signal probe in the User Plane, and (ii) control messages monitored by the CP signal probe in the Control Plane.
